<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It's a common practice to call dirname multiple times to require the TestHelper file from a parent directory.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
require_once dirname(dirname(dirname(__FILE__))) . '/TestHelper.php';
</code></pre>

<p>The code above should be replaced with the following one</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
require_once dirname(__FILE__) . '/../../TestHelper.php';
</code></pre>

